{
  "stem": "20686.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave us enough to-- not to die, but not to live.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Upper Silesia, we had the same thing as in Auschwitz but a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a few more potatoes in the soup, and you know, after all, we were a working team.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they didn't want to lose the-- the labor force.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was no conditions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just were driven out to-- to the place of work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, we-- we started to work under the supervision of-- of kapos and-- of German staff.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started about I think 7:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We worked till about till-- till the sunset, till there was no more light in the day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no specific hours-- specific hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this particular camp, I think it was about 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small camp, maybe 1,500.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course people died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hunger, starvation, exhaustion, beating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, we went, once the Russians start moving, and-- on the front line of central Europe, they took us from there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was taken to a camp Ebensee in the mountains, Austrian mountains, in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was probably the horriblest camp I ever been to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was never-- I couldn't see the light.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in a-- in a forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't remember seeing the sky there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huge, perhaps, primordial trees, so big giants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
